# Hyperlinks

## Strong (Primary Action Links)
Used for: "Create an account", "View All", "Learn More", "View Breakdown"
```
text-[#004299] hover:underline font-semibold
```

## Subtle (Secondary/Auxiliary Links)
Used for: "Forgot Password", "terms of use", "privacy policy"
```
text-[#004299] hover:underline font-normal
```

## Size Rules
- Default: `text-[12px]` in body copy, cards, compact layouts
- Standalone: `text-[14px]` for prominent links
- In larger text: match parent text size

## Interactive Links (Inside Consent/Cards)
```
text-[#00b8f5] font-semibold hover:underline
```

## Teal Accent Links (Drawers)
```
text-[#00b8f5] font-semibold hover:underline
```
Used for: "Need Help?", "Download", "Reward Points Payment Detail"

## Rules
- Always `hover:underline` for clean appearance
- Hyperlinks default to navy blue `#004299`
- Only hyperlink text inside charges column gets `font-semibold` — see `payment-settings.mdc`
- Never use `text-decoration: underline` as default state
